{"tid":1790750,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"楊潤雄：將涉違規教師停職絕非未審先判","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T11:01:39.000Z","uid":216992,"like":12,"dislike":169,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"16856b4f9baf8030222e178e139a528253dbad2b","tid":1790750,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:34:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局局長楊潤雄指，過去一段時間有小部分教師違規，令專業教育工作者蒙羞，教育局將指令學校更加嚴肅跟進老師違規行為，強調將違規教師停職，絕非未審先判。<br />\n<br />\n教育局向全港學校發信，指令學校更嚴肅處理教師與學生的違規行為，若不跟從，局方會主動跟進，而六月中至今，局方共收到123宗與教師專業操守有關投訴，已完成74宗調查，當中30宗不成立，31宗初步認為有機會成立，已經向多名教師發譴責信和警告信，提醒教師若再犯失德行為，會被取消教席。"},{"pid":"44051be812ef9d9dcc76819f36e21661c6d99975","tid":1790750,"uid":216992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:35:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374078&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Z1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=7007b663\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D374078&h=729f8fbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=374078</a>"},{"pid":"49b01ca12acb94d735a0607a7704de4145be28f9","tid":1790750,"uid":216992,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"唔係未審先判 咁係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文革？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文字獄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asse