不跟從，局方會主動跟進，而六月中至今，局方共收到123宗與教師專業操守有關投訴，已完成74宗調查，當中30宗不成立，31宗初步認為有機會成立，已經向多名教師發譴責信和警告信，提醒教師若再犯失德行為，會被取消教席。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"30宗係藍師 所以完全唔洗調查都可以不成立"},{"pid":"a632ad2af2bddbcb4e27caf6839a6cf2202f07a9","tid":1790750,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:08:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b5f184d779977ec593fb67d94eedf1b0eb4386d","tid":1790750,"uid":309503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:08:58.000Z","msg":"香港過一半人返你哋<br />\n蒙你老母"},{"pid":"f151f2ba5b98f6832b70f77c844ab7ac345652f1","tid":1790750,"uid":126306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:09:04.000Z","msg":"返校<br />\n楊狗忠心愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e40a760446b7750cdb2bcf5aa45a2c634404d6","tid":1790750,"uid":4973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"我哋未審先判唔係未審先判<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39ecf0ab0444429130a01b324b21841fe13d3461","tid":1790750,"uid":216992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64e40a760446b7750cdb2bcf5aa45a2c634404d6","tid":1790750,"uid":4973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"我哋未審先判唔係未審先判<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bcc7b9d6bbdf5c9071bed82fca3735fc7c489c4","tid":1790750,"uid":93383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"共: 未審先判絕非未審先判"},{"pid":"cb1c7ba2568ef58bdffe9a3d111630ed1fd863cf","tid":1790750,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"等制裁啦<i